: 0.9985079288940859, \"rank\": 0.0014942973592370046, \"text\": \"Milan\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\"}, {\"begin\": 191, \"end\": 198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.04770564778285e-13, \"text\": \"Cortina\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\"}, {\"begin\": 199, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2026_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2026 Winter Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2026_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2026_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 254, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 0.9515739490559701, \"rank\": 0.05079535517323649, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Hockey Hall of Fame has since deniedthe request, emphasizing that the Hall of Fame is a nonprofit organization and items on display are in fact considered charitable donations.\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughes and Team USA defeated Canada 2-1 in OT with a shot at the 1:41 mark to give the U.S. men their first Olympic gold since the Lake Placid Miracle on Ice in 1980.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 474, \"end\": 480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9999264447151597, \"rank\": 7.345376178409222e-05, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 488, \"end\": 490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Operating_Thetan\", \"score\": 0.9999532021202191, \"rank\": 4.5788446292141504e-05, \"text\": \"OT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Operating_Thetan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Operating_Thetan\"}, {\"begin\": 532, \"end\": 536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998530258559717, \"rank\": 0.00013251875054428065, \"text\": \"U.S.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, the Hockey Hall of Fame began displaying both Hughes' overtime \\\"golden goal\\\" puck and that of Megan Keller, whose overtime goal delivered the Olympic gold medal as well to theAmerican women's hockey team.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9987047435807547, \"rank\": 0.0011513756299136014, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Keller\", \"score\": 0.9999993486210162, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Megan Keller\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Keller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Keller\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pucks are featured in an \\\"Olympics '26\\\" display that also contains a captain Hilary Knight Team USA jersey and a stick used by American teammate Brady Tkachuk, among other various Olympic items.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 911, \"end\": 924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilary_Knight_(ice_hockey)\", \"score\": 0.8930669237582849, \"rank\": 0.11973684210525959, \"text\": \"Hilary Knight\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilary_Knight_(ice_hockey)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilary_Knight_(ice_hockey)\"}, {\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9999699775489999, \"rank\": 3.002335225687715e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999712957169069, \"rank\": 1.6032045421639365e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 979, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brady_Tkachuk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brady Tkachuk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brady_Tkachuk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brady_Tkachuk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vice president of the resource center and curator of the institution said legal bindings surrounding the puck(s) in reference have already been set in stone.\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unfortunately, in the easiest words, it was never Jack's puck to own,\\\" Philip Pritchard, vice president of the resource center and curator for the Hockey Hall of Fame,told ESPN per Greg Wyshynski.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1244, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.9999988583064956, \"rank\": 1.13343509336475e-06, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}, {\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.9075124109327286e-12, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}, {\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Wyshynski\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greg Wyshynski\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Wyshynski\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Wyshynski\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been donated to us now.\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For every artifact that's been donated, we have a paper trail and signed paperwork of where it's come from ... Part of being a nonprofit registered charity in Canada is it becomes kind of a legal document that we have received it as a donation.\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1580, \"end\": 1586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9999264447151597, \"rank\": 7.345376178409222e-05, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have insured it, we have preserved it, we conserved everything.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It becomes part of our institution.\\\"\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughespreviously told ESPNhe wants his puck back, but had not yet put in an official request with the Hockey Hall of Fame.\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am trying to get it.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like, that's bulls--- that the Hockey Hall of Fame has it, in my opinion.\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why would they have that puck?\\\"\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughes asked.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not see why Megan Keller or I should not have those pucks.\\\"\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2057, \"end\": 2069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Keller\", \"score\": 0.9999993486210162, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Megan Keller\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Keller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Keller\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The recent Olympic tournament was a joint production by both the International Olympic Committee and the International Ice Hockey Federation, with there already being an established artifact donation process through the IIHF.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2171, \"end\": 2202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2211, \"end\": 2246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Ice_Hockey_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Ice Hockey Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Ice_Hockey_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Ice_Hockey_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Items are formally transferred to the Hall through IIHF's established artifact donation process and added into our permanent collection.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These artifacts are preserved, exhibited and shared with fans worldwide through our museum and international outreach programs, ensuring that defining Olympic and World Championship moments are preserved, and remain accessible to the global hockey community,\\\" the Hall of Fame said in a statement.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughes is a Florida native and has 51 points across 17 goals and 34 assists this season with New Jersey.\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2770, \"end\": 2776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9987047435807547, \"rank\": 0.0011513756299136014, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 2782, \"end\": 2789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\", \"score\": 0.995360283032169, \"rank\": 0.004592650368258099, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\"}, {\"begin\": 2863, \"end\": 2873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey_Devils\", \"score\": 0.9999999954789018, \"rank\": 4.520015379253058e-09, \"text\": \"New Jersey\", \"types\": [\"Q4498974\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey_Devils\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey_Devils\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pritchard also said that the purpose of the Hockey Hall of Fame is to preserve a game that \\\"Jack's lucky enough to play.\\\"\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2968, \"end\": 2972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.9999988583064956, \"rank\": 1.13343509336475e-06, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since returning from Italy, the Devils' member recordeda hat trick over the New York Rangerson March 7.\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3019, \"end\": 3024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9989329804220812, \"rank\": 0.0010676343993162114, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We try to take the emotion out of it.\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are here to preserve a game that Jack's lucky enough to play or we are lucky enough to work in,\\\" Pritchard said.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's why the Hockey Hall of Fame museum exists as an institution: We are preserving the game of the past, present and the future.\\\"\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Make sure you bookmark Breakaway On SI for the latest news, exclusive interviews, recruiting coverage, and more!\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3416, \"end\": 3425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breakaway_(Kelly_Clarkson_album)\", \"score\": 0.7716166552236794, \"rank\": 0.22961373390559284, \"text\": \"Breakaway\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breakaway_(Kelly_Clarkson_album)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breakaway_(Kelly_Clarkson_album)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 3507, \"to\": 3533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Jennifer Streeter graduated with a B.A.\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3633, \"end\": 3637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bachelor_of_Arts\", \"score\": 0.9970136598548003, \"rank\": 0.0026153762185577908, \"text\": \"B.A.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bachelor_of_Arts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bachelor_of_Arts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"in journalism from Texas A&M and received her Master of Science from Columbia University's Graduate School of Journalism.\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3657, \"end\": 3662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Texas_at_Austin\", \"score\": 0.9771106813273982, \"rank\": 0.023250864223408486, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Texas_at_Austin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Texas_at_Austin\"}, {\"begin\": 3663, \"end\": 3666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Henson_Company_Lot\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.818049322397422e-16, \"text\": \"A&M\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Henson_Company_Lot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Henson_Company_Lot\"}, {\"begin\": 3707, \"end\": 3726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_University\", \"score\": 0.9999903331098489, \"rank\": 9.598278716900986e-06, \"text\": \"Columbia University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At both schools, she focused on an emphasis of sports reporting.\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A former athlete herself, \\\"Jenny\\\" was a varsity soccer player and comes from a family who participated in NCAA athletics.\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 3946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3931, \"end\": 3935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.998974227395263, \"rank\": 0.00102670223006249, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has covered everything from the 2025 Hughes Bowl, SEC football, Ivy League athletics, the 2023 ALCS and the 2023 World Series, the WNBA, and much more.\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 4102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4001, \"end\": 4004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeastern_Conference\", \"score\": 0.9996158968011934, \"rank\": 0.0003842507906891659, \"text\": \"SEC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeastern_Conference\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeastern_Conference\"}, {\"begin\": 4082, \"end\": 4086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.392069093260081e-15, \"text\": \"WNBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2\\u00a9 20262024 ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 4210, \"to\": 4286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ a